Bacterial DNA was extracted with a DNeasy PowerSoil Kit (Qiagen, Hilden, Germany). Real-time PCR was performed in a total volume of 20 µl, composed of 10 µl of Power SYBR Green Master Mix (Applied Biosystems, Foster City, CA, USA), 1 µl of DNA, and the following universal bacterial 16S rRNA primers: 27F (AGRGTTTGATCMTGGCTCAG
39 , 40
) and 338R (TGCTGCCTCCCGTAGGAGT
